<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Password Reset Request - Dental Kit Store</title>
  </head>
  <body role="main">
    <h1>Password Reset Request</h1>
    <p>Hello {{email}},</p>
    <p>We received a request to reset your password. Click the link below to set a new password:</p>
    <p><a href="{{resetUrl}}" aria-label="Reset your password">Reset Password</a></p>
    <p>If you did not request this, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
    <hr>
    <p>&copy; {{year}} Dental Kit Store</p>
  </body>
</html> 